name: Ruby Setara
goal: I am a student activist seeking to learn more about policies related to young people around the world. My goal is to be a youth advocate for my fellow young people.
interests: Culture, Education and training, Employment and Social Affairs, International co-operation and development
euInitiatives: I am part of the Global Issues Network, and will be going to a conference on Children's Issues to give a presentation on policy related  to young people. I think that there is much we can learn from one another; as an American, with family originally from Bangladesh, I know we are not as informed of European policies and practices as we should be. Similarly, I hope that I can provide some insight from my perspectives and experiences.
